      "versionNonce": 1116295869,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773248337576,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Q IF one big company like Google bought other company like Youtube, How Google services will\n    communicate with Youtube.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q IF one big company like Google bought other company like Youtube, How Google services will\n    communicate with Youtube.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NTaOOLl_fochpPM_Uud55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1344.8057332963417,
      "y": 37072.92091767791,
      "width": 1001,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "baO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 997726515,
      "version": 139,
      "versionNonce": 1260258301,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773248405669,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Using VPC tunnel, it is a secure tunnel. basically alllowing Google VPC to communicate with\nYoutube VPC.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Using VPC tunnel, it is a secure tunnel. basically alllowing Google VPC to communicate with\nYoutube VPC.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Oi5gtvlno-8g5TxnZBtpa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1277.4658895463417,
      "y": 37164.27638642791,
      "width": 847,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "baP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1143007421,
      "version": 104,
      "versionNonce": 1254686653,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773248501870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Q If two clouds are different cloud Like AWS and GCP? How we can communicate?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q If two clouds are different cloud Like AWS and GCP? How we can communicate?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "swKkiM8cENrd21xd2iSez",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1335.7783895463417,
      "y": 37203.13576142791,
      "width": 1023,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "baQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1550408755,
      "version": 257,
      "versionNonce": 302455101,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773248584989,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "we can also communicate, but first we need to setup communication between these 2 cloud, once\nwe are able to set up communication between these 2, then one is 1 VCP and other is other VCP\nand we can communicate via VCP tunnel.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "we can also communicate, but first we need to setup communication between these 2 cloud, once\nwe are able to set up communication between these 2, then one is 1 VCP and other is other VCP\nand we can communicate via VCP tunnel.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Y8AbfQoFyk_JAht6RDQak",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1267.3760457963417,
      "y": 37356.18654267791,
      "width": 1144,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "baR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1153563731,
      "version": 189,
      "versionNonce": 1210745715,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773249354778,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In Our AWS account we can see a VPC is always create, we have created other resource or not , or whether\nthis account is completly new.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In Our AWS account we can see a VPC is always create, we have created other resource or not , or whether\nthis account is completly new.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "t8vnpZ0IFYzZCbKNj4KHp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1264.8369832963417,
      "y": 37485.24513642791,
      "width": 264,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
