      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773642383928,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "the storage that we use for mounting or attaching as a Hardisk to our system. In the cloud we will see\nthere are storage server, big storage server. From this storage server they will give us part of HDD\nmounted or attached to our VM. So this storage be it the built in storage or the additional storage\nthat we are adding, this kind of storage is called as block storage. Why it is diff, Because we can\ndo mounting, partitioning, formatting, basically we have control on partition table, file system table\nand everything.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "the storage that we use for mounting or attaching as a Hardisk to our system. In the cloud we will see\nthere are storage server, big storage server. From this storage server they will give us part of HDD\nmounted or attached to our VM. So this storage be it the built in storage or the additional storage\nthat we are adding, this kind of storage is called as block storage. Why it is diff, Because we can\ndo mounting, partitioning, formatting, basically we have control on partition table, file system table\nand everything.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
