      "updated": 1773642419420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "IAAS(Infrastructure as a service) ->",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "IAAS(Infrastructure as a service) ->",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vDoWzu4MwDo-WhxPDKuC4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1256.743233296342,
      "y": 42027.41115205291,
      "width": 1056,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bbe",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2035488086,
      "version": 976,
      "versionNonce": 1086419094,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773642826554,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In PASS we are getting bunch of softwares but what if we want the command on our core hardwares\nalso where these softwares are running, We want to select particular OS, we want OS environments\nto be changed, or OS variable to be changed, We want OS to have few additional sofwares or if\nwe want to partition disk in a certain way or change the disk size stuff like that, we dont be \nable to do it in PASS. For this we need a whole system whole VM like thing where in we want the\ncontrol on OS also or we want to use softwares or deply my applications also, we want to use \nstorage over there also. Monitor which software runs on which part of the processor and all the\nstuff like that. To do it basically we need control or command on complete Virtual Machine So \nproviding them whole VM or any stuff like that it is called as Infrastructure as a service.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In PASS we are getting bunch of softwares but what if we want the command on our core hardwares\nalso where these softwares are running, We want to select particular OS, we want OS environments\nto be changed, or OS variable to be changed, We want OS to have few additional sofwares or if\nwe want to partition disk in a certain way or change the disk size stuff like that, we dont be \nable to do it in PASS. For this we need a whole system whole VM like thing where in we want the\ncontrol on OS also or we want to use softwares or deply my applications also, we want to use \nstorage over there also. Monitor which software runs on which part of the processor and all the\nstuff like that. To do it basically we need control or command on complete Virtual Machine So \nproviding them whole VM or any stuff like that it is called as Infrastructure as a service.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aoFSpzJ_4avsZYBmPF1-X",
