    {
      "id": "UFYUIHj_C0Z9bF53iFXc4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1237.497139546342,
      "y": 42523.21193330291,
      "width": 1177,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bbj",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 249785482,
      "version": 433,
      "versionNonce": 1112251338,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773643187190,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Where in database is already stored or already installed, We can go there and run few queries and after\nrunning few queries our DB server is there. We dont have to separately install the DB server, WE can create\nour own database and tables. we dont have to separately install and manage the Database that will be\nup and running always.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Where in database is already stored or already installed, We can go there and run few queries and after\nrunning few queries our DB server is there. We dont have to separately install the DB server, WE can create\nour own database and tables. we dont have to separately install and manage the Database that will be\nup and running always.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Ll9z8gXwDoWPj0l6y007P",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1196.079170796342,
      "y": 42700.68849580291,
      "width": 1188,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bbl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 883554314,
      "version": 232,
      "versionNonce": 124612938,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773644041542,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Question -> We can have IAAS, we have a VM, In this VM we can also put softwares and we can start using that\n, In this VM also we can also put database and start using it then why to have these service separately?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Question -> We can have IAAS, we have a VM, In this VM we can also put softwares and we can start using that\n, In this VM also we can also put database and start using it then why to have these service separately?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uQ-GZlJ781OxBRfQaZjLd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1226.919014546342,
      "y": 42769.93849580291,
      "width": 1133,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bbo",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2089936854,
      "version": 557,
      "versionNonce": 1056916042,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773644283204,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "First of all cloud will manage the creation of my whole DB, inside that we can put run database command\nbut database server whihc means installing SQL or making sure that SQL is continuously running, that \npart is not outsource from cloud making sure that system on which I am running SQL, it is constantly\nup and running that part is outsourced to AWS or Google cloud or any other cloud that we are using that\nis outsource to Cloud Provider.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "First of all cloud will manage the creation of my whole DB, inside that we can put run database command\nbut database server whihc means installing SQL or making sure that SQL is continuously running, that \npart is not outsource from cloud making sure that system on which I am running SQL, it is constantly\nup and running that part is outsourced to AWS or Google cloud or any other cloud that we are using that\nis outsource to Cloud Provider.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "pf1vOk_a26WhvxRSUa6U7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1231.161202046342,
      "y": 42927.25099580291,
      "width": 1133,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bbq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1133950922,
      "version": 871,
      "versionNonce": 1111671382,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773645258908,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What if my DB goes down or data needs a backup so for all those purposes things get simplified for us\nthat is why we use this as a service where in we only have to focus on creating tables or running other\nqueries and stuff like that, there are many services like that for example there is cache container \nas a service which provides Docker containers\nIOT as a Service or AI as a service so there are many more services, major one that we need to focus on\nis \n\nSAAS\nPASS\nStAAS\nIAAS\n\nALot of other servies, eventually they become a subclassification of one of these. Very few are there\nwhich are separate from being one of these of subclassification of one of these four services",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What if my DB goes down or data needs a backup so for all those purposes things get simplified for us\nthat is why we use this as a service where in we only have to focus on creating tables or running other\nqueries and stuff like that, there are many services like that for example there is cache container \nas a service which provides Docker containers\nIOT as a Service or AI as a service so there are many more services, major one that we need to focus on\nis \n\nSAAS\nPASS\nStAAS\nIAAS\n\nALot of other servies, eventually they become a subclassification of one of these. Very few are there\nwhich are separate from being one of these of subclassification of one of these four services",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
