      "versionNonce": 509695690,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773646119198,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In this what is crucial that that we should understand is that who can talk to whom and how? or\nwhom we need to give permissions?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In this what is crucial that that we should understand is that who can talk to whom and how? or\nwhom we need to give permissions?",
      "autoResize": true,
