      "seed": 1556833120,
      "version": 490,
      "versionNonce": 662485664,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773830021153,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "IN heart beat checking we not only check which server is running or not, we also check which server\nhas howmuch load. So according to our requirement we will set pre configuration like\n\nif utilization of all server < 50 % then reduce the instance\nif utilization of all sever > 80% add a new instance\n\naccording to pre configuration LB will add and reduce the instance we no need to do anything.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "IN heart beat checking we not only check which server is running or not, we also check which server\nhas howmuch load. So according to our requirement we will set pre configuration like\n\nif utilization of all server < 50 % then reduce the instance\nif utilization of all sever > 80% add a new instance\n\naccording to pre configuration LB will add and reduce the instance we no need to do anything.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
