      "versionNonce": 1500618400,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773831345615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How We will tell our LB after launching instance go inside instance and start my Apache Server\nor start my Backend server or my database server\n\nWhat we will do here, \n    we will create a instance, will do all our modification like security and all and make \n   a AMI from this, this AMI will later be used, So everytime now it is launching a instance\nwith my given details and my given AMI our applicatoin automatically start ho jaegi, because\nthat is set in our AMI already\nSo this is work for autoscaling.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How We will tell our LB after launching instance go inside instance and start my Apache Server\nor start my Backend server or my database server\n\nWhat we will do here, \n    we will create a instance, will do all our modification like security and all and make \n   a AMI from this, this AMI will later be used, So everytime now it is launching a instance\nwith my given details and my given AMI our applicatoin automatically start ho jaegi, because\nthat is set in our AMI already\nSo this is work for autoscaling.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
