      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773849395620,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "where we dont need entire OS level control. But the control on OS also of different types, If we need\ndeeper control on our OS then we have entire VM, But if we need some basic control like we need to\nrun 2 3 application together and then only it will work, just in those cases we can use something like\ncontainers also. For container there are diff technologies we can use docker, we can use Kubernetes, \nall of stuff we will talk about later on.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "where we dont need entire OS level control. But the control on OS also of different types, If we need\ndeeper control on our OS then we have entire VM, But if we need some basic control like we need to\nrun 2 3 application together and then only it will work, just in those cases we can use something like\ncontainers also. For container there are diff technologies we can use docker, we can use Kubernetes, \nall of stuff we will talk about later on.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
