      "text": "Make 2 EC2 instances one is FE server and other is BE server in BE we need to write an API that\nis returing Hello to whomever it is calling, this API will be called by this FE server. Wherein \nthere is a test button, we willl become user and hit this test button this will communicate to\nour backend system and this backend system will return Hello to this test and this test again \nwill be displayed on browser to the user as a HTML code or page.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Make 2 EC2 instances one is FE server and other is BE server in BE we need to write an API that\nis returing Hello to whomever it is calling, this API will be called by this FE server. Wherein \nthere is a test button, we willl become user and hit this test button this will communicate to\nour backend system and this backend system will return Hello to this test and this test again \nwill be displayed on browser to the user as a HTML code or page.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
