      "updated": 1775965097377,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now back Read DB have multiple Read replicas, and all these are copy of my write DB. So that all those\nmillions of customer, I am handling via scaling my read DB that would not a issue for us. At the same\ntime single write DB.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now back Read DB have multiple Read replicas, and all these are copy of my write DB. So that all those\nmillions of customer, I am handling via scaling my read DB that would not a issue for us. At the same\ntime single write DB.",
      "autoResize": true,
