    {
      "id": "R0FjAav9-j508JSvv7wke",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2112.4996625684735,
      "y": 77809.09305137482,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "blr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1693380316,
      "version": 545,
      "versionNonce": 1817765084,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776002447015,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Our Frontend LB will keep on writing\nmessage or request here, every data\nthat LB is writing over we will add\none more thing which is topic. we will\nadd topic like if the message is of this\ntopic add this topic. there is a built\nin feature for this. and Pipeline will\npull these messages.\nour ML engines will keep on pulling\nthis in some interval.\nif the topic is of that machine\nthen it will take that message else\nmove to other machine.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Our Frontend LB will keep on writing\nmessage or request here, every data\nthat LB is writing over we will add\none more thing which is topic. we will\nadd topic like if the message is of this\ntopic add this topic. there is a built\nin feature for this. and Pipeline will\npull these messages.\nour ML engines will keep on pulling\nthis in some interval.\nif the topic is of that machine\nthen it will take that message else\nmove to other machine.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1ruyFYPpz0dnk1Sz-dSWW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1815.3603115718392,
      "y": 78220.80766807974,
      "width": 1133,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bls",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 669535452,
      "version": 273,
      "versionNonce": 188114916,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776002635066,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Q At the end Message Queue is also a machine, and machine has a storage, and storage get full, So how a\n storage managed in a message queue, this is very important part",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q At the end Message Queue is also a machine, and machine has a storage, and storage get full, So how a\n storage managed in a message queue, this is very important part",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uN3afFbD00eH_ByL6R15I",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1902.9035823876197,
      "y": 78197.21594834115,
      "width": 11,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "blt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2049640796,
      "version": 5,
      "versionNonce": 1256029020,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776001221931,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "gcfBYZeejWUQOM25LIe3A",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1849.616374064971,
      "y": 78275.59529112192,
      "width": 1111,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "blu",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 281915356,
      "version": 426,
      "versionNonce": 2003290980,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776002635066,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "To manage the storage what we will usually do, we will try to delete the messages, because these are\nuseful, we can't randomly delete them, so there are two kind of deletion mecahnism that we usually\napply, one is TBD, another one is RBD. which usually keep my queue empty or keep the load on my queue\nis less.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "To manage the storage what we will usually do, we will try to delete the messages, because these are\nuseful, we can't randomly delete them, so there are two kind of deletion mecahnism that we usually\napply, one is TBD, another one is RBD. which usually keep my queue empty or keep the load on my queue\nis less.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TBeWMRB6C0N3IBXJQ3Pll",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1848.5861165463805,
      "y": 78403.85826386296,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "blv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2141687004,
      "version": 75,
      "versionNonce": 782286564,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776002635066,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TBD(Time Based Deletion) ->",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TBD(Time Based Deletion) ->",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9kbsOt-tqSOuEoB9Y1xiX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2156.011689434974,
      "y": 78401.13544042097,
      "width": 836,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "blw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 919674076,
      "version": 573,
      "versionNonce": 158286436,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776002635066,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "it says according to time define lets say 5 minute or 10 minute or anything\nafter that delele that message automatically. If the pipeline is not reading\nin that much time. then we will assume no Pipeline that requires this topic\nor pipeline is deleted. First we set more time lets say 30 minute or 1 hour\nand slowly we observer in how much time message is read according to that \nwe will set 5 more buffer minute.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "it says according to time define lets say 5 minute or 10 minute or anything\nafter that delele that message automatically. If the pipeline is not reading\nin that much time. then we will assume no Pipeline that requires this topic\nor pipeline is deleted. First we set more time lets say 30 minute or 1 hour\nand slowly we observer in how much time message is read according to that \nwe will set 5 more buffer minute.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5scs_YFyAWqrX9OO2SQ6F",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1836.8853347281035,
      "y": 78645.48835366218,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "blx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1183710564,
      "version": 93,
      "versionNonce": 513889764,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776002635066,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "RBD(Read Based Deletion) ->",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "RBD(Read Based Deletion) ->",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "InhgUyFtqcCCTu7Z801RI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1903.9501932001565,
      "y": 78691.46972791449,
      "width": 1188,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bly",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1561319652,
      "version": 659,
      "versionNonce": 2068117860,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776002635066,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "like we know we have one pipeline that uses topic A, we have two pipelines that uses topic C and we have\ntwo pipeline that used topic B. So we will configure like if A is read once delete it automatically, dont\nwait for 10 minutes to expire. Once A read is complete read means not only topic read , message pull is also\ndone, delete it immadiately, when B read twice delete it, when C read twice delete it , this is Read based\ndeletion. Queue works on FCFS basis. so first message will be pulled first delete first.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "like we know we have one pipeline that uses topic A, we have two pipelines that uses topic C and we have\ntwo pipeline that used topic B. So we will configure like if A is read once delete it automatically, dont\nwait for 10 minutes to expire. Once A read is complete read means not only topic read , message pull is also\ndone, delete it immadiately, when B read twice delete it, when C read twice delete it , this is Read based\ndeletion. Queue works on FCFS basis. so first message will be pulled first delete first.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
