      "originalText": "Because these ML algo are heavy in nature so\nthey are in EC2 mostly. we can continerise them\ndockerise them and we can deploy. If it is a tiny\nML algo, we can deploy them as lambda.\nIf it is a heavy ML algo,try and choose a complete\nEC2 instance.",
